BBB Model QikProp BBB Model (QikProp) implemented here is from Jorgensens QikProp program using 104 training compounds. This model was validated against 240 Wyeth compounds with known measured B/P ratio and a good correlation with experimental results was observed (R2=0.65).Recommendation: A BBB value of 1 indicates BBB penetration, while value of 0 indicates no BBB penetration. VAL_NUM 110
BBB Model Wyeth BBB Model (Wyeth) is an in-house model for predicting BBB, which was developed using 240 in-house compounds. The model was validated against published categorical dataset of ~1000 CNS compounds where 80% of the known CNS active compounds and 75% of CNS inactive were classified correctly. Recommendation: A BBB value of 1 indicates BBB penetration, while value of 0 indicates no BBB penetration. VAL_NUM 111
